0 You can sell or buy some stuff here. The top row shows your belongings, the bottom row shows what you can buy. To make a purchase, click on the item using the central button, select quantity using left and right buttons, then select "Accept" in the right softkey menu. In order to buy and sell faster, you can use the "Dial / Cancel max" button (click on any item and press this button - the maximum allowed number of copies of this item will be selected for purchase / sale. If you press it again, this number will be reset to zero). The button "Select / Cancel all" allows you to select all items from the hero's bag for sale, pressing it again removes the selection.
1 - Number "7" is the number of items in your bag.
2 - Number "12" is the number of items selected.
3 - The left bottom corner shows the item's race.
4 - "142" indicates the price.
5 - Number "3" shows the item's level.
6 - The items you can put on are marked with a green tick. You can use only those items that belong to friendly races. The item's level must not exceed yours for you to be able to use it.
7 - The items that you cannot put on are marked with a red cross. However, you can take them away with you, sell or exchange these items.
